		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://irfankhawajaphilosopher.com/2020/03/28/coronavirus-diary-20-its-going-to-be-just-fine/" rel="bookmark">Coronavirus Diary (20): &#8220;It&#8217;s Going to Be Just&nbsp;Fine.&#8221;</a></h1>
				<div class="entry-meta">
			Posted on <a href="https://irfankhawajaphilosopher.com/2020/03/28/coronavirus-diary-20-its-going-to-be-just-fine/" title="10:01 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2020-03-28T22:01:23-04:00" pubdate>March 28, 2020</time></a><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://irfankhawajaphilosopher.com/author/khawajaenator/" title="View all posts by Irfan Khawaja" rel="author">Irfan Khawaja</a></span></span><span class="cats-links"> under <a href="https://irfankhawajaphilosopher.com/tag/covid-19/" rel="category tag">COVID-19</a></span>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
		
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

